Class DefaultOHLCDataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jfree.data.general.AbstractDataset

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.ObjectInputValidation, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.EventListener, Dataset, SeriesChangeListener, SeriesDataset, OHLCDataset, XYDataset, org.jfree.util.PublicCloneable

    public class DefaultOHLCDataset
extends AbstractXYDataset
implements OHLCDataset, org.jfree.util.PublicCloneable
    A simple implementation of the OHLCDataset interface. This implementation supports only one series.
